{{zh-forms|[[一生受用不尽]]|[[一]][[生]][[受]][[用]][[不]][[盡]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' yī shēng shòu yòng bù jìn)
# reap the benefits of something for the rest of one's life
#: ''[[他]][[當年]][[對]][[我]][[的]][[一番]][[教導]]，[[讓]][[我]]'''一生受用不盡'''.''
#: ''The guidance and instruction that he gave me in those years is something from which I will '''reap the benefits for the rest of my life'''.

